  "description": "<p>招聘：美容院临时助理（短期）</p><p>📍 Kovan – Solace Wellness</p><p>⏰做几天（可商量）</p><p></p><p>工作内容：</p><p>* 打扫美容房、整理毛巾、补充用品</p><p>* 顾客前准备及事后房间整理</p><p>* 柜台接待、倒水、通知美容师</p><p>* 接电话、回复简单信息</p><p></p><p>要求：</p><p>✔ 爱干净、有礼貌</p><p>✔ 有责任感、准时</p><p>✔ 不需要美容经验（会教）</p><p></p><p>💰 时薪 $XX（可商量）</p><p></p><p>有兴趣请 PM 我 97973248<br /></p><p>===========================</p><p><strong>Hiring: Temporary Beauty Salon Assistant (Short-Term)</strong><br />📍 <strong>Kovan – Solace Wellness</strong><br />⏰ <strong>Work for a few days (negotiable)</strong></p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Cleaning treatment rooms, organizing towels, replenishing supplies</p></li><li><p>Preparing rooms before clients and tidying up after treatments</p></li><li><p>Front desk reception duties, serving water, informing therapists</p></li><li><p>Answering phone calls and replying to simple messages</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />✔ Clean and well-mannered<br />✔ Responsible and punctual<br />✔ No beauty experience required (training provided)</p><p>💰 <strong>Hourly pay: $XX (negotiable)</strong></p><p><strong>Interested? Please PM me 97973248</strong></p>",
